                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable H</hi> 17). I was on duly in Union-street, and took the prisoner, and have the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I had been to Poplar—I saw the handkerchief on the pavement, and took it up—I saw a gentleman coming towards me—I gave it to him, and went away.</p>
